      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p><strong>BharatNotes</strong> (<a href="https://bharatnotes.com">bharatnotes.com</a>) is a free, open-access educational resource for UPSC Civil Services aspirants, created by Bharat Choudhary. We do not require user registration, login, or any personal information to access our content.</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

      <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
      <p>BharatNotes does not collect any personal information directly. We have no sign-up forms, no login system, and no contact forms that store data on our servers.</p>

      <h3>Automatically Collected Information</h3>
      <p>We use <strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong> to understand how visitors use our site. Cloudflare Web Analytics is privacy-first and:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Does <strong>not</strong> use cookies</li>
        <li>Does <strong>not</strong> track individual users across sites</li>
        <li>Does <strong>not</strong> collect personal information</li>
        <li>Collects only aggregate data: page views, referrers, countries, device types</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Local Storage</h3>
      <p>BharatNotes uses your browser's <strong>localStorage</strong> (not cookies) to save your preferences and progress locally on your device. This includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Syllabus tracker progress</li>
        <li>Prelims tracker progress</li>
        <li>Bookmarked topics</li>
        <li>Vocabulary and key terms progress</li>
      </ul>
      <p>This data never leaves your device and is not sent to any server. You can clear it at any time from the <a href="/tracker/">Tracker</a> page or by clearing your browser data.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

      <h3>Google AdSense</h3>
      <p>We use <strong>Google AdSense</strong> to display advertisements. Google AdSense may use cookies and web beacons to serve ads based on your prior visits to this and other websites. Specifically:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Google uses the <strong>DART cookie</strong> to serve ads based on your visits to BharatNotes and other sites on the internet</li>
        <li>You may opt out of personalised advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a></li>
        <li>You may opt out of third-party vendor cookies by visiting <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">aboutads.info</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>For more information on how Google uses data, see <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener">How Google uses data when you use our partners' sites</a>.</p>

      <h3>Google Fonts</h3>
      <p>We load fonts (DM Serif Display, Plus Jakarta Sans) from Google Fonts. Google may collect your IP address and browser information when fonts are loaded. See <a href="https://developers.google.com/fonts/faq/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Fonts Privacy</a>.</p>

      <h3>Cloudflare</h3>
      <p>Our site is hosted on <strong>Cloudflare Pages</strong>. Cloudflare may process your IP address and request metadata for security and performance purposes. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>BharatNotes itself does <strong>not</strong> set any cookies. However, third-party services (Google AdSense, Google Fonts) may set cookies in your browser. You can manage or block cookies through your browser settings.</p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>BharatNotes is an educational resource and does not knowingly collect any personal information from anyone, including children under 13.</p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Since we do not collect personal data on our servers, there is no personal data to access, modify, or delete. Your localStorage data is fully under your control — clear it anytime via browser settings or the Tracker page.</p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this policy, reach out via <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/epicbharat/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>.</p>

